| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2023-1556 — Recovery Inhibition (lockbit3)"
| comment "Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: a15bf044-c08c-56c4-b06e-a5e19d9cab6e"
